<p>Send a photo. Then finish these — 4 to 6 sentences.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>I built the …</p>
<p>The lowest block is at (x = …, y = …).</p>
<p>For a row I changed the … number; to go up I changed the … number.</p>
<p>The hardest square to read was …</p>
<p>Once my picture was wrong because …</p>
<p>Next time I would …</p>
</blockquote>
