<h2>4 · Record Your Walkthrough 🎥</h2>
<p>Film yourself showing your head. Use these words: <strong>x</strong>, <strong>y</strong>, <strong>coordinate</strong>, <strong>across</strong>, <strong>up</strong>, <strong>home spot</strong>.</p>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>Show your home spot. Why stand on it every time?</li>
<li>Show your head from the front.</li>
<li>Point at one block: "this one is at x …, y …".</li>
<li>Show one block you fixed.</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Plan what you will say:</strong></p>
